@model IEnumerable<Carwale.Entity.CompareCars.HotCarComparison>
@using Carwale.Entity.CompareCars
@using Carwale.UI.Common;
@if (Model != null && Model.Any())
{   
	HotCarComparison topCar = Model.First();
	<div class="container"><div class="grid-12 margin-bottom20"><h2 class="text-uppercase text-center margin-top30 margin-bottom10 m-special-skin-text">compare cars</h2><div class="comparo-swiper swiper-container swiper-container-horizontal swiper-container-android"><ul class="swiper-wrapper">
					@foreach (var item in Model)
					{
						<li class="swiper-slide front swiper-slide-visible swiper-slide-active"><div class="contentWrapper"><div class="font11 text-medium-grey position-abt pos-right5 pos-top5">@(item.IsSponsored ? "Ad" : "")</div><div class="comparo-imageWrapper swiper-imgLoader imageWrapper"><a href="/m/comparecars/@item.CompareUrl/" data-role="click-tracking" data-event="CWInteractive" data-cat="Comparison-widget" data-action="Primary-Comparison-m-Click" data-label="@item.HotCars[0].MakeName-@item.HotCars[0].ModelName-vs-@item.HotCars[1].MakeName-@item.HotCars[1].ModelName" onclick="window.location.href = this.href +'?c1=@item.HotCars[0].VersionId&c2=@item.HotCars[1].VersionId&source=@item.WidgetPage';return false;"><img class="lazy padding-top10" data-original="@Carwale.Utility.ImageSizes.CreateImageUrl(item.Image.HostUrl, Carwale.Utility.ImageSizes._357X114, item.Image.ImagePath)" title="@item.HotCars[0].MakeName @item.HotCars[0].ModelName vs @item.HotCars[1].MakeName @item.HotCars[1].ModelName" alt="@item.HotCars[0].MakeName @item.HotCars[0].ModelName vs @item.HotCars[1].MakeName @item.HotCars[1].ModelName" src="" style=" display:inline;"></a></div><p class="font14 text-center padding-top15 padding-bottom10"><a href="/m/comparecars/@item.CompareUrl/" class="text-grey" data-role="click-tracking" data-event="CWInteractive" data-cat="Comparison-widget" data-action="Primary-Comparison-m-Click" data-label="@item.HotCars[0].MakeName-@item.HotCars[0].ModelName-vs-@item.HotCars[1].MakeName-@item.HotCars[1].ModelName" onclick="window.location.href = this.href +'?c1=@item.HotCars[0].VersionId&c2=@item.HotCars[1].VersionId&source=@item.WidgetPage';return false;">
										@item.HotCars[0].MakeName @item.HotCars[0].ModelName vs @item.HotCars[1].MakeName @item.HotCars[1].ModelName
									</a></p></div></li>
					}                   
				</ul><div class="clear"></div><!-- Add Pagination --><div class="swiper-pagination swiper-pagination-white swiper-pagination-clickable swiper-pagination-bullets"><span class="swiper-pagination-bullet swiper-pagination-bullet-active"></span><span class="swiper-pagination-bullet"></span><span class="swiper-pagination-bullet"></span></div><!-- Navigation --><div class="swiper-button-next swiper-button-white"></div><div class="swiper-button-prev swiper-button-white swiper-button-disabled"></div></div><div class="text-center margin-bottom10"><a class="font14" href="/m/comparecars/all/" data-role="click-tracking" data-event="CWInteractive" data-action="AllComparisonButton_HP_Click" data-cat="comparecars" data-label="AllComparisonButton_HP_Click">View more comparisons</a></div></div><div class="clear"></div></div>
}
